    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3 variants · 2 sizes · 5 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Confirmation primitive — specialized modal for "Are you sure?" prompts.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">default · informational</span>
